[OpenAI](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OpenAI) has been moving towards an [Initial Public Offering](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Initial_public_offering) (IPO), where it's for-profit subsidiary OpenAI Group PBC may be listed on a public stock exchange.&#x20;

During 2025, it has been reported that OpenAI is [targeting 2026-2027](https://www.reuters.com/business/openai-lays-groundwork-juggernaut-ipo-up-1-trillion-valuation-2025-10-29/) for their IPO, aiming to raise at least \$60 billion with a valuation of \~\$1 trillion.

If OpenAI is successful in raising that amount of money, it would be the [largest IPO in history](https://siliconangle.com/2025/10/29/openai-reportedly-planning-2026-2027-ipo-valuation-1t/), exceeding both Saudi Aramco and Alibaba.

Following a long public discourse, it has now been announced by FIFA president Gianni Infantino that [Iran will participate in the 2026 FIFA World Cup hosted in the USA. ](https://www.theguardian.com/football/2026/apr/30/iran-world-cup-gianni-infantino)

Team USA is part of Group D with the Iranian team being part of group G.&#x20;

While in the Group stage it's impossible for the two teams to meet, there are many different ways for the two teams to meet in the knockout rounds.

